org.apache.hadoop.hbase.io.compress.zstd

Class ZstdCodec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.io.compress.zstd.ZstdCodec
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.CompressionCodec

    @InterfaceAudience.Private
public class ZstdCodec
extends Object
implements org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.io.compress.CompressionCodec
    Hadoop ZStandard codec implemented with zstd-jni.

    This is data format compatible with Hadoop's native ZStandard codec.
